{"url": "people.com/tv/kourtney-kardashian-still-thinks-sofia-richie-too-young-scott-disick/", "text": "Scott Disick\u2018s girlfriend Sofia Richie is 15 years his junior \u2014 and the age gap continues to raise eyebrows.\n\nA source tells PEOPLE that Disick\u2019s ex Kourtney Kardashian, 39, still thinks Richie, 19, is \u201ctoo young\u201d for Disick, 34. That being said, the source adds that as long as the coupling helps keep Disick on track, they have Kardashian\u2019s blessing.\n\nRichie and Disick have been officially dating since last September after initially sparking romance rumors a year ago. In recent months, the relationship appears to have gotten increasingly serious, with Richie spending plenty of time \u2014 and even vacationing \u2014 with Disick and Kardashian\u2019s three children: sons Mason, 8, Reign, 3, and daughter Penelope, 5.\n\n\u201cSofia is helping Scott be a better, healthier person,\u201d the source tells PEOPLE. \u201cKourtney feels confident that Scott and Sofia takes good care of the kids. Scott is a great dad when he has his life together.\u201d\n\nWant to keep up on the latest from PEOPLE? Sign up for our daily newsletter to get our best stories of the day delivered straight to your inbox.\n\nPaul Archuleta/FilmMagic; Mat Hayward/Getty Images; Matteo Prandoni/BFA/REX/Shutterstock\n\nEarlier this year, an insider told PEOPLE that Kardashian didn\u2019t react positively to the romance at first.\n\n\u201cLike most people, she thinks Sofia is way too young for him and doesn\u2019t get it,\u201d the insider said.\n\nAccording to the insider, Kardashian, who is currently dating 25-year-old Younes Bendjima, initially assumed it was just a fling when she found out her ex had moved on with Richie.\n\n\u201cKourtney didn\u2019t think it would last and she never thought Sofia was going to meet her kids,\u201d the insider said. \u201cBut now, Sofia spends a lot of time at Scott\u2019s, so Kourtney allowed her to meet the kids.\u201d\n\nRELATED VIDEO: Kendall Jenner Shades Scott Disick and Girlfriend Sofia Richie\u2019s Age Gap on Instagram\n\nAs for Disick? He thinks it\u2019s \u201ckind of flattering\u201d that people care about his love life.\n\n\u201cIt\u2019s not like I\u2019m mad about it,\u201d he told PEOPLE in March while hosting a party at Jewel nightclub in Las Vegas. \u201cEverybody\u2019s worried about something. Everybody is worried about other people\u2019s things, so it\u2019s fine.\u201d", "images": ["https://people.com/thmb/LztNjwaQ-ix4eK4edUooLhNiWi4=/800x533/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/anna-kepner-3-111025-c6a90b2f57474459a89ae04e296ec343.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/ntoAw_fxEWplb5ZgDI3nJ3b4DoM=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/reign-disick-scott-disick-111125-53c441afa43246d7b6e030ff73143477.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/0bvo74qf8rt6loEWC_ZHtk0V-mc=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/ines-de-ramon-brad-pitt-jay-kelly-los-angeles-premiere-111225-1-9585e8fd85a548fa8a065a588d2b2aa2.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/6UIRVs8M7vPGvO1ErgwQpN4RsJQ=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/kristin-cavallari-tout-6c06282a8e794cce8a0f3a5e5ba8bb11.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/YUbZglSf0-xLdBce4icfuzRj2fs=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/dakota-johnson-1-110325-27dbdbcc4fc141e48f98af697b2f8c40.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/CnnGOYzk0tFWm4Tg2kNMnHbU-wk=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Gigi-Hadid-Bradley-Cooper-Eagles-111825-01-6878aecbf8794d1b8e88c36ea8ed865a.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/RHWCVsKuwdFve_po2zfkNoOuDec=/4000x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(999x0:1001x2)/scott-disick-c19517a15d27499e8c4888fb7d309ade.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/JdDtMMRJJqIFYiRgVYaypBKxb6Y=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/diplo-katy-perry-justin-trudeau-110325-2070f21d8543497886ea6b27932f259e.jpg", "https://people.com/th